These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, turquise, yellow, red
There 4 different types of food: carrot, garlic, pineapple, peas
1. the person who likes turquise is between the person who likes lilac and the person eating garlic##2
2. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
3. the person who likes turquise is somewhere between the person who likes red and the person who likes lilac##7
4. the person eating garlic is in an even position##4
5. the person who likes red is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
6. the person eating garlic is somewhere to the left of the person eating carrot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Color   | yellow | red       | turquise | lilac        |
| Food      | pineapple  | garlic | peas        | carrot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, van, trike, boat
4 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, bridge, whist
1. the person playing whist is somewhere between the person playing bridge and the person driving the trike##7
2. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
3. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
4. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
5. the person playing whist is between the person playing bridge and the person playing billiard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Transport     | trike | van       | boat         | scooter     |
| Game   | billiard   | whist | bridge | monopoly |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, dunhill, blend, montecristo
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, may, january, september
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in april##7
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the dunhill-smoker##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Cigar   | dunhill | montecristo | blend | davidoff  |
| Birthday   | january | april  | september   | may |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, coffee, juice
4 different pets are kept: fish, ferret, rabbit, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the owner of the ferret and the person drinking juice##7
3. the person drinking coffee is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | sprite | cola | juice       | coffee |
| Pet   | ferret      | fish   | rabbit | guinea-pig  |

