.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, fantasy, romance, action
4 different pets are kept: dog, cat, bird, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
2. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
6. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
7. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre         | romance | martial-arts   | action | fantasy |
| Pet   | dog      | cat | chinchilla      | bird |

