.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, tram, jet-ski, ship
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, september, january, june
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is the person driving the ship##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
6. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in september##7
7. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Transport      | tram | skateboard      | jet-ski | ship     |
| Birthday   | march    | june | september   | january |

