.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, monopoly, billiard
There 4 different types of food: cherry, apricot, cabbage, orange
1. the person playing backgammon is not the person eating orange##6
2. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
3. the person playing billiard is the person eating cabbage##1
4. the person playing monopoly is somewhere between the person playing billiard and the person playing scrabble##7
5. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
6. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
7. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Game   | billiard | monopoly | backgammon | scrabble |
| Food           | cabbage   | orange    | cherry       | apricot  |

