.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, ice-hockey, rugby, skateboarding
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, lily, bellflower, daisy
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the person who growsiris##6
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who growsdaisy and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##7
6. the person who growslily is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbellflower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Sport           | skateboarding | snowboarding | rugby | ice-hockey |
| Flower   | daisy         | bellflower      | iris | lily            |

