.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike, airplane, boat
House: victorian, wooden, craftsman, ranch-style
1. the person driving the boat is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the ranch-style house##7
2. the person driving the quad-bike is not the craftsman house##6
3. the wooden house is not the person driving the airplane##6
4. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the ranch-style house##5
5. the person driving the scooter is the victorian house##1
6. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Transport   | scooter | boat | quad-bike | airplane |
| House           | victorian    | wooden   | ranch-style  | craftsman      |

