3. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the futuristic house##5
4. the craftsman house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
5. the farmhouse house is between the colonial house and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
6. the owner of the lizard is somewhere between the owner of the guinea-pig and the colonial house##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| House   | craftsman | farmhouse | colonial | futuristic   |
| Pet   | guinea-pig    | lizard      | goldfish      | frog |

