.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, grey, green, light-blue
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, surfing, rugby, golf
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who likes green##1
4. the person who likes green is not the person who's sport is surfing##6
5. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who likes green##7
7. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Color       | light-blue | fuchsia | grey | green |
| Sport   | weightlifting   | golf      | surfing        | rugby  |

