3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
4. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4
5. the person eating pear is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##5
6. the person eating pear is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
7. the person eating spinach is the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Food      | pear   | garlic | spinach | grapes   |
| Birthday   | may | september   | april | august |

