2. the dutch is on the right of the british##1
3. the fan reggae is on the left of the fan pop##1
4. the british is somewhere to the right of the fan indie##5
5. the fan indie is on the left or right of the american##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Music-Genre         | electronic    | indie | reggae     | pop |
| Nationality   | american | indian  | british | dutch |

 